Police where extremely confused on Friday night when they pulled Adelaide small forward Tyson Stengle over. Police were initially baffled by how close his name was to Tyson Stenglein and ran a license check which confused them more as he was registered to both adelaide and west coast. 
"What the fuck is going on mate" 
"what are you talking abeet" 
"Does he play for Adelaide or West Coast?"
"I dunno moit"
"Just charge him with un-registered vehicle"
"Aight"
"Wait, why did we pull him over"
"Cause he's pissed mate"
"oh yeah, is he hell pissed?"
"Yeah nah yeah"
"Ok just charge him with being beersy and unregistered"
"Easily"
